info.author: Maarten van Gompel <proycon@anaproy.nl>
info.name: sesdiff
info.summary: Generates a shortest edit script (Myers' diff algorithm) to indicate how to get from the strings in column A to the strings in column B. Also provides the edit distance (levenshtein). This is the Python binding.
